# 12 Audit Evidence and Documentation

## Intent
Ensure compliance controls are demonstrable through durable evidence artifacts.

## Mandatory Evidence Sets
- Processing records and data-flow maps.
- DPIAs/threat models for high-risk features.
- Consent records and DSAR case logs.
- Incident reports and notification decisions.
- Vendor assessments/contracts and transfer documentation.
- Security testing reports and remediation tracking.

## Operational Rules
- Evidence artifacts must have owner, timestamp, and retention policy.
- Evidence must be discoverable by service/plugin and release version.

## Release Blockers
- Missing evidence for any required control domain.
